eaned up the language here, but the original videos are saltier.=0A=0A[2] I=
ncidentally that coin is called =E2=80=9CJosh Allen MVP.=E2=80=9D Josh Alle=
n did in fact =0Awin the National Football League=E2=80=99s Most Valuable P=
